name: GOING TO LIGHT
description:
when i was young, sometimes when I fall asleep, I dream of seeing my body sleeping in my room.
the condition of the room at that time was dark but from behind the door I could see the light. when I opened the door, I was suddenly in a Chinatown area and walking alone.

after a few years later from the dream, I came to the Chinatown area in the city where I live and saw the same pattern when I had a dream.

miraculously this photo is quite similar to the one I dreamed of
